insert  into `SECRETARIAT`(`secretariat_ID`,`position`,`first_name`,`last_name`,`email`,`bio`) values 
(1,'Secretary-General','Siddharth','Kumar','secgen@ilmunc-india.com','<p>Siddharth is a sophomore studying Computer Science in the School of Engineering and Applied Sciences. Hailing from Bangalore, Siddharth can’t wait to return to India this fall as the Secretary General of ILMUNC India. Outside Model UN, Siddharth loves to play golf, do volunteer work, listen to music and watch House of Cards! Siddharth attended ILMUNC India in 2014, and as an alumnus of the conference he couldn’t be more excited to meet you all and help shape your ILMUNC India experience.</p>'),
(2,'Director-General','Noah','Levine','dirgen@ilmunc-india.com','<p>Noah, your Director-General, couldn’t be more excited to welcome you all to ILMUNC: India 2017! He was an Under-Secretary General for Crisis Committees at Penn’s college-level MUN conference; he is also a Deputy Director on  Penn’s intercollegiate MUN team. Outside of Model UN, you can find Noah playing any sport competently but by no means well, drinking amounts of coffee which can best be measured in gallons, and bringing up random facts about anything that he finds interesting. He’s getting hyped for conference - and so should you!</p>'),
(3,'Chief of Staff','Elena','Zhou','staff@ilmunc-india.com','<p>Elena is a junior in Wharton, studying finance and operations concentrations with a minor in math. While she calls Richmond, VA her home, she was born in China and is a Canadian citizen. She could not be more excited to be serving as your Chief of Staff for ILMUNC India this year. When she\'s not attending ILMUNC India meetings, you can find her eating papaya, watching Suits, or exploring Philly\'s coffeeshops. Elena is super excited to meet you all at conference and ready to make ILMUNC India 2017 absolutely, hands-down, without a doubt, insanely incredible!</p>'),
(4,'Chief Operating Officer','David','Wang','operations@ilmunc-india.com','<p>David is a junior in the School of Engineering at the University of Pennsylvania, pursuing a major in Computer Engineering and a minor in Entrepreneurship. Though originally born in Canada, he has lived in rural New Hampshire for the majority of his life. David\'s Model UN career began in high school, and has continued well into his time at Penn. Currently, he serves as a Head Delegate and the Chief of Development for Penn’s competitive MUN team. Outside of MUN, he is involved in PennApps, a student-run hackathon, and the university orchestra. In his spare time, he enjoys biking, backpacking, and photography. He can\'t wait to meet you all at conference! </p>'),
(7,'Business Director','Lucia','Game','admin@ilmunc-india.com','<p>Lucia is a Junior at the University of Pennsylvania majoring in Systems Science and Engineering. She was born in Washington DC but moved around South America, living in Colombia, Bolivia and Ecuador, where her family is originally from. Other than being an MUN geek, Lucia is also obsessed with drones and transportation, and works as an undergraduate researcher at Penn. Her favorite pass times are binge watching Netflix, dancing to latin music, and trying new restaurants around Philly. She is very excited to be joining you this year as Business Director for Ilmunc India, and can’t wait to be part of such an amazing conference.</p>');
